Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个兵器拥有打破世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将世界引同灭亡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像巴哈姆特一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱紧我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得故乡的奶奶说过以前经常去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去妮娜的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禀报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越狱的贞德·达克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗·雷欧涅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜·朵兰格的行踪目前还未查到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘的小孩的情况也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已对凯撒·利德法尔德进行过拷问了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他什么都设说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是奥尔良骑士团的团长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多练练再来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越狱犯就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去艾博斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要见你 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亚思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢房生活已经步入正轨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起铁栏杆 你还是更适合握剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士团情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长都被抓了 还能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亚思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔良骑士团就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见到贞德大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔良骑士团必将复活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要让骑士团跟贞德大人一起重获荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给贞德大人和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能直接叫妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 妮娜回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 瞅瞅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是莫拉 叫瞅瞅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何叫瞅瞅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我朋友 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在王都流行这种衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要丟下你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我故乡的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是贞德...达克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是摆设哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你变瘦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朋友贞德说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 你去过神界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我们怎么去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吗 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥...自便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2000年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神与恶魔齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了巴哈姆特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时背着精疲力尽的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将他们回到了神界的正是老朽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来啦 又是这一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我当年的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 帅气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是迷上老朽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这背 怎么坐嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何都要去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还望您助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 睡着就叫不醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的温泉可厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能疗伤 还能去除疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹的爸爸帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还叫那位大人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟恋爰不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 小孩不是爱的结晶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人 如今仍在守护着我和艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有倾心的男性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要接近帅气的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成龙大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此一直无法跟倾心的人好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 唯独能跟那人一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟他在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至觉得我来到世上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了跟他跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是初恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德的初恋是怎样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在春心萌动之前就收到了启示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以神的仆人的身份上战场了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的仆人不能恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿妮娜能跟那人过上幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我也不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明人超好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然干了那么多可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此仍然喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我依然无法恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中也有多个面目各异的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有两张相反的面目也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妮娜能爱上他的所有面目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份恋情也许就是真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好看得很 好看得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜要待多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要去趟神界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神界？我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不是说去就去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去神界干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去见姆伽罗妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗妹妹是贞德的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是失散的神圣之子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣之子？什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,编吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家就是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣之子就是神圣之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是问你神圣之子是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝水的话 那里有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话 要聊几句吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是个很神奇的村子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次来也很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不是龙族来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山脚的村子出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是嫁过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜真是个好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 寄养在我们家的孩子们的父母画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子的日子也不好过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都出去赚钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜的父亲也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的父亲已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 为了保护村子不被火球砸中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子有没有突然变龙你们添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 她救了我们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 那孩子也长大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自从父亲死的那天开始就变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要靠近跟她父亲年纪相仿的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成龙大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不去回想痛苦的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你当她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这人根本不值得感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对妮娜的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看过她有多亲近你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你对妮娜有多好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:18:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都喊你收敛点了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻耳子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候就该说那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要娶你当团长夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊 团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 副团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是奥尔良骑士团的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不就开个玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 刻耳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩睡好没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡得可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真打算去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 要怎么去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 坐我背上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你那小身板...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:20:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带着天使回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 路上当心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好保护贞德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就突破极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 你擅长什么料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然提起这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长什么啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之都 P1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长什么啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 咋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用汤煮菜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是汤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还望下集继续关照